com.google.api.client.googleapis.subscriptions

Class Notification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.client.googleapis.subscriptions.Notification
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TypedNotification, UnparsedNotification

    public abstract class Notification
extends java.lang.Object
    Beta
    Notification sent to this client about a subscribed resource.

    Implementation is thread-safe.

    Since:
    1.14
    Author:
    Matthias Linder (mlinder)
